FBIS3-2459 "drchi046_k_94035" FBIS-CHI-94-046 Document Type:Daily Report 9 Mar 1994 NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political & Social Foreign Women Experts Mark Womens Day in Beijing OW0803103094 Beijing XINHUA in English 0935 GMT 8 Mar 94 OW0803103094 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Beijing, March 8 (XINHUA) -- Some 50 foreign women experts gathered here today to mark the 84th anniversary of the International Women's Day. Tian Shulan, a leading official of the All-China Women's Federation (ACWF), gave them a briefing on how Chinese women participate in economic construction and on the ACWF's efforts to expand international exchanges. According to the State Bureau of Foreign Experts, some 1,500 women experts from 30 countries now work in colleges as well as cultural, publication and news organizations throughout China.
